  <title>Moving fields</title>
  <para>
    The fields may be placed in different regions of the form. To move a field the user can access the
    contextual menu of the field and select 'Move field'.
  </para>
  <figure>
    <title>Move field option</title>

    <screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/FormModeler/11_movefield.png"/>
        </imageobject>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot>
  </figure>
  <para>
    This will display the different regions of the form where you can place it.
  </para>
  <figure>
    <title>Destination areas to move the field</title>

    <screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/FormModeler/12_move_areas.png"/>
        </imageobject>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot>
  </figure>
  <para>
    A field can be moved to the first or the last region with the contextual icons for that purpose.
  </para>
</section>
